################################################################## THE ARTIST ###############################################################

terminal when (J_Artist) {
text: [[TTRS:notrans=
░▒▒█░▒▓▒▓███▒▓█░▒▓▒█▓█▓░▒█░░
▒█ALL ARTISTS ARE WARRIORS▒█
███▒███░▒▓█░██████▒█▒▓▓█▓░▒█
▓▒█OF THE ETERNAL CITY▓▓██▓▒
█░█▒█████▓░▒██▒▓▓░█████▒███▒

You are Athena
   the Artist, born of the mind
   blessed & condemned to be the voice of the past
   (eternity is in love with the productions of time)
   
The hazy ghost of Weariness is always upon you, breaking your will.
You fear that you may fail before the Great Work is finished.
But there is hope:
       In the fire of your hearth
       you have seen the TREE OF LIFE.
The sap of this tree will give you the strength to finish the Great Work.

]]
options:{
"TTRS:notrans=Seek the Tree" next: J_SeekTree
    }
}

